title: Silent_Decay - King Of The Death End Road (2009)
description:
Silent Decay was a modern metal band from Munich. Originally the band started with a mixture of Thrash Metal and Death Metal, built over time, but more and more modern elements from the fields of neo thrash, screamo or metalcore one.

This is the last album released in 2009 they did before the group in 2010!
